  "prompt": "Is there a Monster Hunter PC game?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several \"Monster Hunter\" games available on PC. The most notable titles include:\n\n1. **Monster Hunter: World** - Released in 2018, it was the first game in the series to receive a major worldwide release on PC and features a more open-world approach and improved graphics.\n\n2. **Monster Hunter Rise** - Released in 2021 for the Nintendo Switch and later on PC in early 2022, this entry focuses on mobility with new mechanics like the Wirebug, which allows for more dynamic movement during hunts.\n\nBoth games received positive reviews and expanded the reach of the franchise on the PC platform. If you are a fan of action RPGs and hunting games, these titles are definitely worth checking out!",
